Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会有小翼能做到但小光做不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要做现在的小翼就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜 翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个不幸的消息要告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.54,0:02:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.29,0:02:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相泽翔同学去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有睡觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭了 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼要是哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:06:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢各位今天不顾风雪来为翔最后送行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔平时很少生病 是个开朗的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定是拜学校与翔和睦相处的各位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悉心教导他的各位老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及各位邻里所赐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为父亲请容我在此向各位道声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然仅是短暂的十年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我深信对于翔来说是充实的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔的各位朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请珍藏起和翔的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远记住和翔在一起的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次感谢各位今天的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(圣诞节蛋糕接受预定)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没有母亲还是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼和小光好像还是没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜想这种时候要是有母亲在的话可以换种鼓励的方式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班上的同学突然去世的确是个打击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲在的话么...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会回答这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有人会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你去换桶里的水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:10:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没怎么吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃饭身体要坏掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有小光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有爸爸能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都可以说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别总是一副阴阳怪气的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相泽同学过世已经二周了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起相处了那么久的朋友突然走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一定都很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也应该一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我觉得如果大家总是这么消沉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定相泽同学知道了反而会更伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以老师今天给大家一个提议
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都写封信给相泽同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都想对相泽同学说的话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是现在才敢说的话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把你心里想对相泽同学说的话写下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得只要试着用你最真诚的心写信给相泽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:13:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就一定能了解对于大家来说相泽同学是个什么样的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生态反应消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你已经习惯了卡利恩刀的使用方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但操作时间还是有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就开始下一个模拟训练吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个比刚才那个玛基的防御力更高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要从正面进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞空艇能量投射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中继能量转换器发射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡利恩刀能量低下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥林蒂娜 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量投射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:14:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量补充开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛基处于攻击状态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生态反应消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量投射系统现阶段只能这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是考虑到要提高卡利恩兵器的攻击力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就需要更大输出量的投射装置了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:15:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 她们两个人怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使现在玛基出现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们也不太可能出战的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关系很好的朋友死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不得已的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我们两个尽力准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 写好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是个好天 带着天丸去散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天丸 走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天丸真精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行不行 不能这么滚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天丸全身都是雪了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没有来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说椎名翼的父亲在这里是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 英 有人找你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 翔的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前些日子麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉 让您特地来这一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼她碰巧不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 是我没打招呼就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来想能当面交还她的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把这个交给小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约三周之前翔和小翼去了气球大会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个时候翔从小翼那里借了这块手绢儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这事儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在班上相处得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔经常在家里提起小翼的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:21:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去气球大会的那天好像玩的特别开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来之后也非常高兴的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这得感谢小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让那个孩子有了那么多美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探测有结果了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在第6只以后的玛基孵化地附近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能发现母体玛基到过的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:21:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.97,0:22:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母体是怎么在那些地方产卵的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.77,0:22:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是卵孵化的空间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要放大了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,线状痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,0:22:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从卵所在的地下再往更深层的地下\N延伸的极细的管道空间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.38,0:22:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于太过细小好像至今都没有被探测到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第6只以后所有的地方都有这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.22,0:22:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个空间是干什么用的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前仅仅是我的猜测
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是用来流通玛基需要的空气以及根的延伸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.23,0:22:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得母体使用了类似空气或者根之类的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.90,0:22:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个地方直接产卵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据这个星球的玛基的生态变化情况来看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么能确定那个线状痕迹到底连着什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 往地下延伸后在中途就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过好像延伸到了相当深的地下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.72,0:23:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定这个线状痕迹的尽头就是母体玛基吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.19,0:23:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先根据脉冲的特性在探测一下更深的地下区域
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.98,0:23:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是由于非常的深
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.32,0:23:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要探测北海道全部区域的话可能要费很多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.82,0:23:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是如果母体玛基真的在那么深的地下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.24,0:23:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它到底在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.70,0:24:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.50,0:24:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天翔的母亲来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.54,0:24:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说要把这个还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.88,0:24:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔的母亲说非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.64,0:24:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说翔是非常重要的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.07,0:25:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.66,0:25:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.58,0:25:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.08,0:25:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么翔的妈妈会来我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.72,0:25:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气球大会？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.14,0:25:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.93,0:25:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以对小翼来说打击更大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.23,0:25:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.45,0:25:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.66,0:25:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过一会去看看她
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.08,0:25:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.50,0:26:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 可可哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.05,0:26:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 喝完了去下看电视吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.97,0:26:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么一起洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.32,0:27:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.36,0:27:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢来没关系可是得打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.54,0:27:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能老是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.79,0:27:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是为了翔打起精神来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.21,0:27:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光不明白我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.30,0:27:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.38,0:27:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是就算你再悲伤翔也不会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.76,0:27:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有班上的同学都很伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.10,0:27:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是总是这么伤心...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.94,0:27:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不努力打起精神来是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.69,0:27:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.70,0:27:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.78,0:27:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我有多痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.70,0:27:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会让我努力打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.49,0:27:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只会说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.29,0:27:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.17,0:28:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 你也...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.88,0:28:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 你也不明白我的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.26,0:28:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气球大会的事为什么瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.47,0:28:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为小翼会什么事都告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.65,0:28:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说你不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.82,0:28:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔就能明白我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.53,0:28:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从不会对我说努力吧什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.37,0:28:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会对我说你现在这样就很好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.25,0:28:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不止这些
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.29,0:28:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野营的时候 文艺会的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.17,0:28:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都有很多话想和他说
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.39,0:28:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多好多事想和他说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.57,0:29:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 我想我有点明白你的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.12,0:29:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为第一次见面时我就拥有了和你相同的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.83,0:29:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后也总是一起哭一起笑
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.17,0:29:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着相同的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.34,0:29:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 小翼的心情...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.09,0:29:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光不明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.68,0:29:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.51,0:29:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小光和我不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.35,0:29:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.02,0:29:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼和我...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.61,0:29:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.49,0:29:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点儿都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.36,0:29:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光不过是拥有了我的记忆而已
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.78,0:30:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那之后我也有了只属于自己的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.54,0:30:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔的事 还有很多其他事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.50,0:30:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果翔还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.71,0:30:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后我还会有更多自己的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.80,0:30:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些你怎么能明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.68,0:30:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你和我根本就不是双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.64,0:30:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你根本就不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.14,0:30:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.55,0:31:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.06,0:31:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是曾经任意地复制了你的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.15,0:31:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅是这样是不可能理解你的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.49,0:31:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.47,0:31:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.39,0:31:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.94,0:31:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.69,0:31:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.95,0:32:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.04,0:32:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.29,0:32:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.63,0:32:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想一直都和小翼在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.22,0:32:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我特别喜欢小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.26,0:32:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是像小翼喜欢翔那样地非常地喜欢小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.06,0:32:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我虽然可能成不了小翼的翔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.53,0:32:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过只要小翼能够恢复精神
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.12,0:32:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.37,0:32:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小翼要是死了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.75,0:32:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样忧郁的死了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.76,0:33:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能也会伤心的死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.56,0:33:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.06,0:33:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.94,0:33:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你也不是真正的姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.90,0:33:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为了小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.03,0:33:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.66,0:33:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神来 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.00,0:33:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 小翼就是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.38,0:33:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论什么时候都会在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.47,0:33:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论什么时候我都会永远在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.36,0:33:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天只能我们两个上了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.44,0:33:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.10,0:34:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡利恩刀的能量补充就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.93,0:34:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.94,0:34:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.23,0:35:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥林蒂娜 投射能量
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.21,0:35:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量补充中断
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.71,0:35:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.96,0:35:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥利蒂娜 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.76,0:35:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.38,0:35:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀里剩下的卡利恩能量是我们最后的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.51,0:35:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.76,0:35:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.54,0:36:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.25,0:36:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥利蒂娜 刀已经不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.09,0:36:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能像以前那样近身撬开外壳了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.34,0:36:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就瞄准那里
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.09,0:36:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.52,0:37:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生态反应消失
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.86,0:37:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.28,0:37:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.79,0:37:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.13,0:37:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.30,0:37:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.46,0:37:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.22,0:37:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们今天的课只有上午的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.06,0:37:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.31,0:38:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.31,0:38:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下午请了假
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.19,0:38:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去翔的墓前祭拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.61,0:38:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都还有话没说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.45,0:38:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 好好去告个别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.75,0:38:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.42,0:38:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那等你们回来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.63,0:38:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.68,0:38:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.30,0:39:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔 能和翔成为好朋友我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.73,0:39:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经和我一起聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.85,0:39:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还教了我很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.15,0:39:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.41,0:39:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远不会忘记和你一起去乘气球的事
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.87,0:40:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然早了点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.91,0:40:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这是全家的圣诞节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.12,0:40:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.46,0:40:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.71,0:40:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐！！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.46,0:40:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个蛋糕好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.55,0:40:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爸爸做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.13,0:40:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然啦 还很新鲜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.39,0:40:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我要分了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.77,0:40:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 去换水桶的水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.86,0:40:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.46,0:41:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名翼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.26,0:41:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.18,0:41:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 很努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.68,0:41:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名光
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.48,0:41:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.74,0:41:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.83,0:41:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前说好的电影去看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.04,0:41:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈说星期天就可以去看
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.50,0:41:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吗 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.71,0:42:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光去的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.18,0:42:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.18,0:42:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么几点在车站集合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.35,0:42:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10点在车站见面
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.47,0:42:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.61,0:42:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说不是普通的地震
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.98,0:42:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据摇晃程度来测算的话
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.28,0:42:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能是工地施工或者房屋倒塌
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.53,0:42:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能是爆炸事件之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.04,0:42:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是完全没有那些事件的报告记录
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.87,0:42:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且最重要的是和那些的波形都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.38,0:42:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能想到是什么原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.55,0:42:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也做了很多调查可是收获甚微
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.47,0:42:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我确实听说
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.22,0:42:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约从二个月前开始这种奇怪的地震就断断续续地发生
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.77,0:42:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.40,0:43:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是不是那个陨石掉落的原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.73,0:43:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陨石？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.19,0:43:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有记录说今年北海道内有多次陨石坠落哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.12,0:43:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.74,0:43:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陨石
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.20,0:43:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没帮上你的忙 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.79,0:43:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,资料数据什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.33,0:43:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候要都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.88,0:43:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.34,0:43:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先让我看看陨石坠落的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.14,0:45:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于小光的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.47,0:45:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼终于能够摆脱那深深的悲伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.39,0:45:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪白的景色中
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.73,0:45:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼和小光的羁绊越来越深
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.73,0:45:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翼 一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.78,0:45:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为有小光陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.20,0:45:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相互了解的心越来越近
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.07,0:45:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短暂的时光却转瞬即逝
